"NetFluss will record per-interface byte counters for %.0f seconds. After you click Start, begin a large download (for example a Speed Test) and let it run until the capture finishes. The diagnostics will then be copied to your clipboard so you can paste them into a GitHub issue.\n\nNo network traffic is sent — only local counters from your machine are recorded." = "NetFluss 将记录每个网络接口的字节计数器 %.0f 秒。点击「开始」后，请启动一个较大的下载（例如速度测试）并让它持续运行至记录结束。诊断信息随后会复制到剪贴板，您可以将其粘贴到 GitHub Issue 中。\n\n不会发送任何网络流量 — 仅记录您机器上的本地计数器。";
"%d snapshots were captured. Paste them into the GitHub issue (issue #31) so the developer can identify which interface accumulates download bytes on your Mac." = "已捕获 %d 个快照。请将其粘贴到 GitHub Issue (#31)，以便开发者识别您 Mac 上哪个接口在累积下载字节。";
